Package com.horse.pokemon.ObjectData.PokemonData Description

The PokemonData package contains PokemonInformation and all calculations that have to do with Pokemon.

Pokemon are creatures that AbstractPlayers capture in order to progress through their journey. These Pokemon contain many different stats such as PokemonInformation.individualValue and PokemonInformation.effortValue. These stats set apart every Pokemon in the Game, adding functionality and reason.

The main aspect of the Game has to do with Pokemon, and leveling them up to stop the antagonists by completing a journey that is stated at the beginning of the Game. The next most prominent part of the Pokemon are that they have Moves, which is used when a User is in a battle with another being.

See Also:
